com.sun.star.uno

Interface IMethodDescription

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IMemberDescription
    Deprecated. 
    This interface does not cover all the features supported by the corresponding (unpublished) implementation. But no client code should need to access this functionality, anyway.

    public interface IMethodDescription
extends IMemberDescription
    The IMethodDescription allows to examine a method in detail. It gives a view to java methods from a UNO point.
